channel.title: Server is down?
channel.description: Is vpsland down or something? I was on my server with like 5 other ppl and all the sudden the vps kicked me off and my server dced.. now it won't lemme connect to my vps and when i go to the control panel it won't lemme view the server info it just says "Server is down" Any help?

item.title: Server is down?

item.description:

[quote=“Usagi, post:2, topic:352222”][font=courier]http://www.vpsland.com/index.php

Try that website, Login and whatever and look for something that says about it being up or down. Restart your computer though I doubt it has anything to do with it. [/font][/quote]

That was retarded.

You are going to have to wait until your VPS stops screwing around, should be fine within a day or so.
